race.comment: CANYA TELL ME (1) is a promising dog yet to miss the frame after four starts including one wins and was in the minors again latest (22.26) over 381m at this track. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. Has the inside draw and looks tough to beat. LET ME BOLT (2) rocketed out of the boxes with a scorching early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (22.21) at this track over 381m. Expected to feature. ELITE ARNOTT (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (22.57) last time in a Novice race at this track. Key player if finds best. BURNING KUNA (3) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.
